    </section>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="docs-code docs-code--html">
  <pre><code class="html">&lt;div class=&quot;Panel Panel--box&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
</div>

<h3>Stacked panels (<code>.Panel--stacked</code>)</h3>
<p>It is possible to make a panel box look as though it is stack on top of others. Useful for tabs and such like.</p>
<p><strong class="Badge">Note</strong> This class musts be used in conjuction with <code>.Panel--box</code>.</p>

<div class="docs-example">
