<h3>Attached panel (<code>.Panel--attached</code>)</h3>
<p>It is possible to attached the panel to other attachable items, for example, the menu (in tabular format) component, to create a tab like component.</p>

<div class="docs-example">
  <ul class="Menu Menu--tabular Menu--attached">
    <li class="Menu-item is-active"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">One</a></li>
    <li class="Menu-item"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">Two</a></li>
    <li class="Menu-item"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">Three</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="Panel Panel--box Panel--attached Panel--stacked">
