<h4>Hidden Panels (<code>.Panels--hidden</code>)</h4>

<p>The hides all of the children panels unless given a <code>is-active</code> class. This can be used with the <a href="switcher.html">switcher</a> module to create simple tabs.</p>

<div class="docs-example">
  <ul class="Menu" data-module="Switcher">
    <li class="Menu-item"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">Panel 1</a></li>
    <li class="Menu-item"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">Panel 2</a></li>
    <li class="Menu-item"><a href="#" class="Menu-link">Panel 3</a></li>
  </ul>

  <div class="Panels Panels--hidden">
    <div class="Panel Panel--box">
      <p>Panel 1</p>
    </div>
    <div class="Panel Panel--box">
      <p>Panel 2</p>
    </div>
    <div class="Panel Panel--box">
      <p>Panel 3</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-code docs-code--html">
  <pre><code class="html">&lt;ul class=&quot;Menu&quot; data-module=&quot;Switcher&quot;&gt;
